      <description>&lt;p&gt;After nearly two years working in the Institute of Nano Science, I decide to leave and head for my next step. I really appreciate the help from my advisor, Prof. Wanlin Guo. He is one of the best teachers I have ever met. Also, I want to thanks the help and appreciations from &lt;a href=&#34;https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=fhdZx6sAAAAJ&amp;amp;hl=en&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Prof. Min Yi&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://scholar.google.com/citations?hl=en&amp;amp;user=NlVmmpgAAAAJ&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Prof. Hu Qiu&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://scholar.google.com/citations?hl=en&amp;amp;user=RA5pOAgAAAAJ&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Prof. Zhuhua Zhang&lt;/a&gt; and lecturer Qing Wang. Importantly, I want to thanks the  accompany of my buddies. Hope you all will have a very bright future!&lt;/p&gt;
